<p><img src="/assets/images/2010/02/4327308293_a0b321676c.jpg" alt="" class="align-center" /></p>

<p>Eating outside in the freezing cold is never a good idea but even taking that into consideration, the beaver tail tasted about as good as it looks in the photo i.e. absolutely terrible.</p>

